conservatrice). Conseiller d'Etat (1841-1847). Avec Josef Leu, il fut l'un des meneurs du mouvement conservateur paysan; il si\u00e9gea au comit\u00e9 central conservateur, mais n'approuva ni le Sonderbund ni le rappel des j\u00e9suites. De tous les membres du gouvernement de 1841, il fut le seul \u00e0 revenir en politique comme juge au tribunal de district (1860-1875) et d\u00e9put\u00e9 au Grand Conseil (1863-1875). Brigadier de la premi\u00e8re division de l'arm\u00e9e du Sonderbund."]], "text_links": [[], [{"start": 12, "end": 20, "mention": null, "origin": "entity_fishing", "annotation": {"wikidata_entity_id": "Q7098", "wikipedia_page_id": 337681, "wikipedia_page_title": null, "wikidata_entity_url": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q7098", "grobid_tag": null, "extra_fields": {"rawName": "Sonderbund", "confidence_score": 0.6451, "domains": ["Administration"], "origin": "entity_fishing"}}, "href": "fr/articles/000615", "dhsid": "000615", "wiki": {"item": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q7098", "itemLabel": "Buchrain", "dhsid": "000615", "namefr": "Buchrain", "articlefr": "https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Buchrain", "namede": "Buchrain LU", "articlede": "https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Buchrain_LU", "nameit": "Buchrain", "articleit": "https://it.wikipedia.org/wiki/Buchrain", "nameen": "Buchrain", "articleen": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Buchrain", "instanceof": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q70208", "instanceofLabel": "commune de Suisse", "gndid": "4687628-5", "wikidata_id": "Q7098"}}, {"start": 34, "end": 42, "mention": null, "origin": "entity_fishing", "annotation": {"wikidata_entity_id": "Q7098", "wikipedia_page_id": 337681, "wikipedia_page_title": null, "wikidata_entity_url": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q7098", "grobid_tag": null, "extra_fields": {"rawName": "Sonderbund", "confidence_score": 0.6451, "domains": ["Administration"], "origin": "entity_fishing"}}, "href": "fr/articles/000615", "dhsid": "000615", "wiki": {"item": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/